750
01:01:44,035 --> 01:01:46,060
<i>So it's just common sense.</i>

751
01:01:47,272 --> 01:01:51,504
<i>So... So how... How do we prevent this?</i>

752
01:01:52,343 --> 01:01:54,470
<i>There's disease, famine.</i>

753
01:01:54,546 --> 01:01:58,346
<i>We generate wars, we plan genocides,</i>

754
01:01:58,983 --> 01:02:03,386
