808
01:07:52,270 --> 01:07:54,170
I'm unloading your car.

809
01:07:55,940 --> 01:07:58,238
You haven't finished your food.

810
01:07:58,976 --> 01:08:00,841
I don't want the food.

811
01:08:02,647 --> 01:08:04,774
You were asking about Simon,

812
01:08:05,616 --> 01:08:08,710
what it was that he was trying to work out.

813
01:08:09,487 --> 01:08:12,581
Lady, we're all trying
to work things out. Okay?

814
01:08:13,491 --> 01:08:16,824
Sabine. You can call me Sabine.

815
01:08:18,663 --> 01:08:19,755
Lady,

816
01:08:22,867 --> 01:08:25,131
you force yourself into my house,

817
01:08:25,203 --> 01:08:29,196
you plan to have me tow your car.
So now I know who you are, and it's over.

818
01:08:32,743 --> 01:08:34,711
You don't know who I am.

819
01:08:35,012 --> 01:08:37,674
Yes, I do. Listen to me.

820
01:08:39,383 --> 01:08:42,750
I was never into plays or drama in school.

821
01:08:42,820 --> 01:08:47,553
I don't understand this pretending stuff.
I don't like this pretending stuff.

822
01:08:48,793 --> 01:08:51,193
You're playing games with people.

823
01:08:51,762 --> 01:08:53,787
That's not what I'm doing.

824
01:08:54,031 --> 01:08:56,431
That's exactly what you're doing.

825
01:08:59,837 --> 01:09:02,829
Simon's parents were killed
in a car accident.

826
01:09:03,174 --> 01:09:05,642
- I told you that.
