835
01:09:49,420 --> 01:09:50,944
at his store.

836
01:09:54,392 --> 01:09:57,156
He was the one who repaired her violin.

837
01:10:04,035 --> 01:10:06,833
The good news is that it's authentic.

838
01:10:09,473 --> 01:10:12,670
The bad news is that... Sorry.

839
01:10:14,612 --> 01:10:19,845
The bad news is that
this whole piece of the violin is new.

