844
01:10:40,705 --> 01:10:43,902
<i>and the angle of the fingerboard
was different,</i>

845
01:10:43,975 --> 01:10:47,035
<i>and then when the new style
was introduced,</i>

846
01:10:48,045 --> 01:10:51,276
