01:11:55,012 --> 01:11:56,809
Look at the drawing.

861
01:11:58,716 --> 01:11:59,705
See?

862
01:12:01,218 --> 01:12:03,209
It would be like this.

863
01:12:03,921 --> 01:12:06,685
